Name:Alpha Werewolf
Desc:The Alpha Werewolf wakes up with the other werewolves and chooses a target to attack with them. At night, the Alpha Werewolf may decide to give the wolves another attack. Any wolves with abilities at night will then not be woken up that night. This can only be done once. Alternatively, the Alpha Werewolf may decide that no role may investigate another player's role or nature. This can also only be done once.
